444
00:33:32,760 --> 00:33:34,387
- Deberíamos cancelarlo.
- Sí.

445
00:33:34,470 --> 00:33:36,139
- Vamos a comer.
- Vale.

446
00:33:38,266 --> 00:33:40,226
