489
00:37:22,406 --> 00:37:23,241
¿Qué?

490
00:37:24,951 --> 00:37:26,202
¿Ojos?

491
00:37:27,995 --> 00:37:28,913
I-na.

492
00:37:46,722 --> 00:37:47,807
Es todo culpa suya.

493
00:37:50,101 --> 00:37:51,310
¿Mía?

494
00:37:51,394 --> 00:37:54,230
